{"id": "1316636819697176617", "channel_id": "1316636819697176617", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168738854837166162", "author_name": "lubi_17667", "author_bot": false, "content": "守密人你好：\n       彌薩格大學校務處將於12月12日13:25進行校內設施修復，更新完成後您將得到通知，重新進入遊戲。對於更新可能給大家帶來的不便，我們會準備一份補給物資以示歉意。祝大家調查順利！ \n\n【補給物資】\n在線維護補償：銀芯*50\n\n【領取條件】\n領取時間截至2024年12月26日23:59。請記得及時前往郵箱領取補給物資哦。  \n\n【更新內容】\n● 修復了部分安卓設備進入「決勝：原初之影」戰鬥後可能會黑屏卡死的問題。（僅安卓用戶會收到本次的更新補丁。）", "timestamp": "2024-12-12T05:24:39.745000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1316636820687159337", "filename": "lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 131424, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1316636819697176617/1316636820687159337/lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg?ex=6a00bf57&is=69ff6dd7&hm=66b9e7efbdf49be689f84df41f61cff69c03ff4045ce9fc01999148f16a5e1bf&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1316636819697176617", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.7.3.1 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
